reviewText: If you like Earnest, you like Earnest! My boys enjoy his antics...
Ernest movies are a good comedy collection.
Great blast from the past for me, my kids love Ernest!
Love his movies . orderd for my brother and he loves them only complaint is theys only two discs so u have to have a remote to change the movie . other than that they are great alot .
Ernest goes to africa did not stand up to the other movies. I haven't had a chance to watch the other ones. I was too disapointed from the first movie.
Jim Varney is funny as usual.  Not as great as his later movies.  But still fun to watch!
